&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fisglobal.com/products/fis-amount?loc=specs&quot;&gt;FIS® Amount™&lt;/a&gt; provides a unified digital origination and decisioning platform that helps financial institutions meet the moment. Designed to scale with banks and credit unions at any stage of their digital journey, FIS® Amount™ delivers a seamless, digital-first experience—streamlining everything from loan origination to deposit account opening. With built-in fraud orchestration and risk management, FIS® Amount™ enables financial institutions to control risk across any product while optimizing performance and enhancing security. Our flexible, modular platform is backed by enterprise-grade infrastructure and compliance, allowing institutions to launch new offerings in months, not years. Learn more at &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fisglobal.com/products/fis-amount?loc=specs&quot;&gt;www.fisglobal.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are FIS. Our technology powers the world’s economy and our teams bring innovation to life. We champion diversity to deliver the best products and solutions for our colleagues, clients and communities. If you’re ready to start learning, growing and making an impact with a career in fintech, we’d like to know: Are you FIS?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Overview:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the Account Specialist for Growth Initiatives, you will be the tactical engine behind our most critical affiliate partnerships. Reporting directly to the Head of Customer Success, you will sit at the intersection of sales enablement, client onboarding, and performance analytics. Your mission is to ensure that partners on platforms like &lt;strong&gt;Credit Karma, Bankrate, and CD Valet&lt;/strong&gt; aren’t just &quot;active,&quot; but are optimized for maximum growth and revenue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Partner Activation &amp;amp; Onboarding&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the &quot;hands-on&quot; onboarding process for new clients, ensuring a seamless transition from sales to active status.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the primary point of contact for daily operations across our core affiliate channels (Credit Karma, Bankrate, CD Valet).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with internal implementation teams to ensure technical setups and changes are accurate and timely.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Sales Enablement &amp;amp; Deal Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide real-time support to the sales team to help close complex deals within the affiliate ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop a deep understanding of each affiliate platform’s unique requirements to guide clients through the nuances of each channel and strategies to run a successful program.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Spearheading cross-functional initiatives to educate the broader FIS sales organization on Amount’s affiliate value proposition&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Performance Optimization&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor partner performance daily to identify trends, bottlenecks, or opportunities for increased volume.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze client data to identify &quot;success stories&quot; that can be turned into case studies or sales collateral.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with the Customer Success Managers to deliver data-backed optimization recommendations to clients that improve their ROI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Cross-Functional Collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide feedback to the Chief Strategy Officer and Head of Client Services regarding &quot;production cohesion&quot;—identifying which product features are needed to drive further affiliate growth.&lt;/li&g

